NAME
    Strava-GPX - Get a gpx file from a strava ride

SYNOPSIS
      use Strava::GPX;
      my $strava = Strava::GPX->new( $url );
      my $gpx = $strava->to_gpx; # gpx file content

DESCRIPTION
    Grab a Strava page, find a course, output a gpx file so you can go ride
    it.

SEE ALSO
    Strava::Utilities

